list.name: Device Status - On
list.query: SELECT body,device_state FROM "sense_event" WHERE ("event_type" = 'new_timeline') and $timeFilter and device_state='DeviceOn'

target.query: SELECT body,device_state FROM "sense_event" WHERE ("device_name" =~ /^$devices$/) and $timeFilter and device_state='DeviceOn'

list.name: Device Status - Off
